name: David Johnson
description: I would describe myself as a caring affectionate, honest man who enjoys keeping in shape. I’m hard working and would like to share time with a special person. I’ve spent time getting to know myself, know what I want and not into games. I’ve attained my goals professionally and financially and would like to share fun times, travel, relaxation, etc. with a special woman. I also like to allow someone to find their fullest potential to do what sets her heart free and to be her authentic self. Finally, I respect the needs of my partner and treat others how I like to be treated. Let’s go out, laugh, have fun and see what happens.
